query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(k mk mi_idx) NoMergeJoin(it1 k mi mi_idx mk t kt) NoMergeJoin(it1 k kt mi mi_idx mk t it2) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS western_dark_production
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('violence',
'corpse')
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '6.9'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND ( t.title like '%murder%' OR t.title like '%Murder%' OR t.title like '%Mord%') AND t.production_year > 1990
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Norwegian',
'America',
'USA',
'Germany',
'Norway',
'Bulgaria',
'Danish',
'Swedish',
'American',
'UK')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'episode'
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating';
